Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:09.03,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord1\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:18.64,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:28.61,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:33.71,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:38.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:51.29,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:01:00.99,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.83,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:11.50,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:20.80,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:33.30,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:58.10,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:01.57,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.33,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.42,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:34.20,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:38.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:40.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:44.77,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:45.98,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:51.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.41,0:23:51.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:57.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:57.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:03.79,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:09.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:14.58,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:00.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find them if you look hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:09.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:12.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like coming back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:14.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it your turn to clean the yard, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:21.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's been half a year since Kanata came to the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotten pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:44.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:52.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can put away those old earplugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:03:00.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame, don't you think you should stay in town this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:08.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:16.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone on this mountain for fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:21.07,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Departure - When the Snow First Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going. Keep going. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to look like a real tank now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you sure you can do the rest yourself, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:38.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My, why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:02.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept the military annuals here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:06.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata wanted to know more about Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where it would be other than there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi might have a copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask next time I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:36.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Iliya was the first daughter of the current Archduke Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:42.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I told you before, but she was an amazing tankman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:47.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus said something like "if she were still alive" when he was here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She passed away. I think it was two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:01.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness was assigned to the royal guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:06.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but she took to wandering the country encouraging national pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:12.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And as she was traveling between cities, she tried to save a drowning child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a rumor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, it's Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:06:01.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She brought Yuuko here - oh, Yuuko is Martin's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:09.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But actually, an old lady named Jacquotte - she lives alone in the mountains -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes I buy vegetables from her in the morning -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:16.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,oh, right! Didn't you say you liked those pickled vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:20.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Jacquotte grew those vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:26.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one has seen Madame Jacquotte recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she hasn't looked very healthy, either, so they're worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:37.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she lives pretty deep in the mountains, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to whatever it is. Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:56.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that Princess Iliya was going to marry the emperor of the holy city, Rome, to improve relations with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:59.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But then she would be the third consort!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The third one! Third!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Practically a bargaining chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:12.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that fell through when she passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:17.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,so we kept fighting until we struck a truce this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A half-built house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say she lived alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:43.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Yuuko sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:49.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:57.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too good for that bratty little Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a wonderful house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I built this house myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That one is for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your son coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in a city far away now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll keep it ready for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:30.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So he and my son can feel at home anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:50.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And when will this son of yours come home, Madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter will come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better leave the mountain before the snow starts falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:12.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish that house. I have no intention to move until I do, or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with this absurd act!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:19.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for winter? Firewood? Food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't prepared anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:27.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work out somehow. Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such nice girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:31.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what a stubborn old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so similar, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that. How am I similar to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:54.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you don't say or listen to what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:09.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report in last week's regular communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roman forces on the eastern borders have been mobilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:22.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:27.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? For Madame Jacquotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take these to her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:51.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you heard anything about how the conferences are going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:54.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Princess Iliya were still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:03.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, Martin. Didn't Princess Iliya have a sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's ¥4,000,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First I've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:12.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she wasn't exactly legitimate, so it was never made public,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:16.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's third in line for the throne or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is her sister-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a little walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your village like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a normal country village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There were plenty of fields and cows and goats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but not many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:58.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... a bit different from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you had good parents too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:10.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of place did you grow up in, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:17.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up in a small village near the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:21.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded by beautiful lakes and forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:27.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived there with just my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:32.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A peaceful, boring life where nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:40.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My only consolation was that my sister -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:45.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,she was born from a different mother - would come to see us sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I admired her more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:54.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was brave, kind, and accepted her fate without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:58.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned the trumpet from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But she... was too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was too kind and gave her life because she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:12.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, I thought this town was a labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:23.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was lost, I came upon this place. I thought I reached some sort of goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But later I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:33.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That this was just a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:36.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to get lost on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:45.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like being lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:51.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! Even if you're lost! Even if it's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I'm jealous of you, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:17.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could be as honest as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:42.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:47.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like her. You're just like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:52.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember bearing a beautiful daughter like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a forbidden love and bore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who might never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:08.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And living that nightmare, my mother passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide that it was a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:23.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised me that he would come back someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:29.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That he would come back for me. I'm content with a promise like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:29.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:40.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If there were anything else, I would have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're content with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you truly happy with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I remember loving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:57.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have my memories of him. Because I have hope to meet him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, I'm content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you think it's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:40.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you, it was snowing like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:54.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Madame was still young, Seize was a thriving resort town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:16.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She fell madly in love with the son of a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:26.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she became pregnant with his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boy already had a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:36.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing or curse, the boy's wife couldn't bear children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:41.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the boy took her child and left for home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:49.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Promising her that he would come back for her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:19.66,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madame! Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:19.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm this old, sometimes I think
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,if only, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.26,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madame Jacquotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Life, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,is just a cycle of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you must find something to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:41.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you do, the pain of loss grows as much as that little happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you have memories of that happiness -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,because you have memories -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,man lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:08.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Sorry it's at a time like this, but I found those pictures of Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when the Princess came to Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Shuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:34.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think my parents wanted me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:39.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,to find a husband and succeed the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:45.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I fell in love with the sound of that trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:48.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:54.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was Iliya, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:59.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:05.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so wonderful. Iliya's sound echoed through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:09.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you and I met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:16.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have run away. To this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So at first, I didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would leave this place one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:31.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I honestly don't want to leave this place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:35.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I must leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's something only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:57.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far apart we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the sound will surely echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:08.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:14.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata. Did I make a good role model?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:18.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Rio left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:44.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She left, echoing within me forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:49.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}the wonderful, wonderful sound of the sky.
